info.name: api v2 Free Tier
info.description:
# Introduction
The purpose of the football-data API is to provide football data in a machine readable way.

# Overview
n/a

# Authentication
You have to pass a custom HTTP header

# Error Codes
403 - You don't have permission to view that resource.
404 - You called a non-existent endpoint.
429 - You should lower your results, you got rate limited.

# Rate limit
See www.football-data.org/documentation/api#request-throttling for detailed information on rate limits. They depend on your plan.
